---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Birth Plan Confidence Session"
  description="Sit down with a certified doula via Zoom and walk through your birth plan line by line. Feel confident, prepared, and ready."
  canonical="https://truejoybirthing.com/birth-plan-session"
>
  <section class="bg-tjb-cream pt-16 pb-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Birth Plan Confidence Session</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-tjb-gray">A line-by-line walkthrough of your birth plan with a certified doula — so you walk in confident, not guessing.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-tjb-cream-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose">
      <h2>What Happens in the Session</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Review your plan against what actually happens in a hospital room</li>
        <li>Discuss the hospitals and providers on your list — what works, what doesn't</li>
        <li>Practice the exact phrases you'll use during pressure moments</li>
        <li>Build Plan B language so you're prepared even if Plan A changes</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-tjb-cream p-6 rounded-xl text-center my-8">
        <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-tjb-lavender-500 mb-2">$250–300</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-tjb-gray mb-4">60–75 minutes via Zoom</p>
        <button class="bg-tjb-lavender-500 text-tjb-cream px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-tjb-rose-500 transition" disabled>Book Now — Coming Soon</button>
        <p class="text-xs text-tjb-gray mt-2">Calendly + Stripe integration in progress. Contact us directly for immediate booking.</p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-tjb-gray italic">Sessions are in high demand. If you need immediate support, email shelbi@truejoybirthing.com.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
